  4. Grad at z_phic_raw is tiny but incl_raw is OK   → φc/ψ-specific issue
  5. If even combo pred gradient is tiny              → loss fn / weighting
  6. If z_phic_raw grad is OK but weights don't move → layer-level (Check 5)


